<subSubSection pageId="62" pageNumber="63" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="62.[151,1437,261,1296]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1197,1224]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">Discussion:</emphasis>
The lone specimen of this species was collected at a rainforest tree trunk flux. As it is a male, it was not ovipositing at this location, but it may have been looking for a female that would be, or simply feeding on the decaying tree sap.
</paragraph>
